text: Lee Jae-nam (born 25 March 1972) is a South Korean rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Asian Games medalists in rowing Category:Rowers at the 1990 Asian Games Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for South Korea Category:Medalists at the 1990 Asian Games
